window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Without royal leadership, Kozalin's defenders are falling into turmoil, but mortal problems pale in insignificance when the Gods themselves take an interest in Daniel. With new enemies appearing everywhere he looks, and far too many secrets to keep, can even Daniel's magic save the day?</p> <p>Well, you know what they say. If you can't get results with violence, you aren't being violent enough...</p> <p>Warning: This novel contains graphic violence, explicit sex, problematic opinions, and a protagonist who has no interest in being normal. Listen at your own risk.</p>"; 
